com.magnet.attributes.api

Interface Data


  • public interface Data
    This is the interface that is used to encapsulate a blob of data.

    • Method Summary

      void dispose()
      Explicitly free any underlying resources and closes the stream.

      Return the mime type associated with this data object.

      Return the String contents (or as much as reasonably possible to fit in memory).
